This home boasts a spacious floor plan flooded with natural light, all bedrooms upstairs, and a deck to entertain.The 2 car garage and a large shed out back provide plenty of storage for equipment, tools or all those holiday decorations.  Recent updates include new flooring, fixtures, paint.Shed and treehouse convey.
